Even if choosing a different URL closing and reeopening it saves the last page.



Reproducible: Always

Steps to Reproduce:
1) Start Mozilla Firefox4.
2) Download any file.
3) Close the application(download process is still on).
4) Reopen the application.
5) See that the last viewed page is not HomePage.
Actual Results:  
As i have said before the last viewed page was opened.

Expected Results:  
To have my HomePage opened.</thetext>
